<h2 id="comparison-with-others">Comparison with Others</h2>
<p><a class="" href="https://sourceforge.net/p/whonix/wiki/Comparison%20with%20Others/#network-time-related">Network Time related</a></p>
<h2 id="external-clock">External Clock</h2>
<p>This topic is still under research. Help is welcome.</p>
<p>It might make sense to add an external clock, such as a GPS, or even better an atomic clock. (Can we get an atomic USB clock?) This clock should be added to the host and/or Whonix-Gateway and/or Whonix-Workstation?</p>
<p>Open question: would the GPS/atomic clock be too accurate and would that make more Whonix fingerprintable?</p>
